import React from 'react'
import {InfoSec} from './infoSection.elements' 
import {Container} from '../../globalStyles'

const infoSection = ({lightBg}) => {
    return (
        <>
        <InfoSec lightBg={lightBg}>
            <Container>
                <InfoRow imgStart={imgStart}>
                    <InfoColumn>
                        <TextWrapper>
                            
                        </TextWrapper>
                    </InfoColumn>
                </InfoRow>
            </Container>
        </InfoSec>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default infoSection
